The body of the 44-year-old boutique hotel employee was found on Tuesday night. CAPE TOWN - Police are investigating the murder of a man at a boutique hotel in Sea Point.The body of a 44-year-old hotel employee was found at Hotel 303 on Tuesday night.He had been shot.The police's Frederick van Wyk says: According to reports a 44-year-old man was shot and killed by unidentified suspects. We ve opened a case of murder for further investigation. No one has been arrested as yet. (Edited by Zamangwane Shange)